<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA13">
<l>vaḻakkoṭu māṟukoḷ ḷaṉṟaṭiyār vēṇṭa</l>
<l>viḻakkavuṅ kāṇṭu miṟaiva viḻappuṇṭē</l>
<l>yemmāṭkoṇ ṭākilum yāṉvēṇṭa veṉkaṇka</l>
<l>ṭammāṟkāṭ ṭuṉmēṉic cāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for falling off from that practice, when [your] servants want [something],</l>
<l>shall we see [them] lose [it] too, o lord, is there a loss?</l>
<l>And if  you have taken us as servants, when I want [it] show [me]</l>
<l>by my eyes the complexion of your body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
